163
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:38,350
Orang bilang cinta menyembuhkan patah hati.

164
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:40,649
Pepatah itu mungkin kuno,

165
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,490
tapi masih bijaksana.

166
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,820
Entahlah.

167
00:08:45,389 --> 00:08:49,129
Akankah dia bersedia menerima orang baru?

168
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:52,159
Karena itu kita harus memancing dia keluar

169
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,629
