177
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:17,690
Baiklah. Tentu.

178
00:09:20,289 --> 00:09:21,320
Kopi?

179
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:25,289
"Putri Oh Jin Sim"

180
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,070
Halo, Nona Oh Jin Sim.

181
00:09:30,299 --> 00:09:31,730
Apa yang kamu lakukan?

182
