jika kita bertiga bertemu.

200
00:10:19,019 --> 00:10:20,149
Kamu mau ikut?

201
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:25,919
Se Won, aku sudah datang.

202
00:10:26,190 --> 00:10:27,259
